## Colocation Rules

1. **Feature-specific components** stay in `[features-folder]/[feature]/components/`
2. **Shared components** go in `[components-folder]/`
3. **Tests** live next to source files (`*.test.[ext]`)
4. **Types** can be in feature folder or shared `[types-folder]/`
